{"tid":317304,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"讀緊中大政政，你問我答","createTime":"2017-07-11T10:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T10:50:37.000Z","uid":39379,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9fafe65b7f4d7d67e128d9005cdd1db74a8442de","tid":317304,"uid":39379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"發問規則<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">夠分嘅就去讀港大啦屌你</span><br />\n2. 唔開名嘅嘢就有求必應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459c14f9cf4ffd93ef3dbfd177de6ee5abac3e8a","tid":317304,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:02:51.000Z","msg":"你d 同學仔有幾多真係對政治有興趣同留意開"},{"pid":"0362083aac8d2e545957a354c10da86639420062","tid":317304,"uid":3823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"主要讀啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋係中大讀呢科同其他u eg poly讀有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20253ee63a77f069f497486db9e8599c9993068","tid":317304,"uid":39379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你d 同學仔有幾多真係對政治有興趣同留意開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個屆一半半 有上系莊或者學生會個啲都會幾上心 立會選舉個排都會出左去助選<br />\n另一半就齋讀書同玩活動<br />\n<br />\n我對落個屆就靜好多嘅...feel like熱衷政治嘅人係少"},{"pid":"21804024c98bb31b7c526c2326278547c49e3b93","tid":317304,"uid":25029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:10:38.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"523249e66a3ed8b34c476cd87afbada2abd39da7","tid":317304,"uid":126336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47f3adefc4ec6e38fb61abde3bff53614c831f39","tid":317304,"uid":25029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你d 同學仔有幾多真係對政治有興趣同留意開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個屆一半半 有上系莊或者學生會個啲都會幾上心 立會選舉個排都會出左去助選<br />\n另一半就齋讀書同玩活動<br />\n<br />\n我對落個屆就靜好多嘅...feel like熱衷政治嘅人係少</blockquote><br />\n同學分清楚，熱衷Politics 不等同熱衷於political science,反之亦然，分清楚</blockquote><br />\n我熱衷後者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b131e91ff95a484ba7a0ad23e344a043b28dd0a","tid":317304,"uid":39379,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>主要讀啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋係中大讀呢科同其他u eg poly讀有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無讀過其他U 答你唔到<br />\n<br />\n讀啲咩呢啲上網自己做功課啦 <br />\n主要分幾類科目嘅 <br />\n包括&quot;政治啲&quot;嘅科eg electoral studies, democratisation <br />\n或者讀公共行政<br />\n又或者國際關係<br />\n又或者係一眾學霸同大愛左膠追捧得好勁嘅政治哲學<br />\n各方面political science嘅嘢都有機會涉獵到"},{"pid":"85a4016e2fc0e409e94d507949e6336ae117ab31","tid":317304,"uid":39379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你d 同學仔有幾多真係對政治有興趣同留意開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個屆一半半 有上系莊或者學生會個啲都會幾上心 立會選舉個排都會出左去助選<br />\n另一半就齋讀書同玩活動<br />\n<br />\n我對落個屆就靜好多嘅...feel like熱衷政治嘅人係少</blockquote><br />\n同學分清楚，熱衷Politics 不等同熱衷於political science,反之亦然，分清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真呀<br />\n識有啲係好中意讀書 成績好好 但係叫佢出黎做政治野就不了"},{"pid":"a2114b79379a60e64eb8c8de213f7ad40af766fb","tid":317304,"uid":44457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"你邊間書院邊間宿"},{"pid":"8883832d81da9b4f106ee45fcf519a4b63229564","tid":317304,"uid":44457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:19:26.000Z","msg":"師兄讀左幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48eb4b01f2a463b3f0d18c7df194aae4a6187a0","tid":317304,"uid":39379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你邊間書院邊間宿</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用建議黎答你：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚揀聯合書院</span>"},{"pid":"c5fe765bb35ccf4cb7846b872d072e0930be3c97","tid":317304,"uid":39379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師兄讀左幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2"},{"pid":"ad8ed32c058b54fc6ebea893fd4390cec2e132af","tid":317304,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你邊間書院邊間宿</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用建議黎答你：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚揀聯合書院</span></blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d90b67fb6d4a0094904016965bf60c8ec1c771","tid":317304,"uid":23562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:26:44.000Z","msg":"點解會被稱為四大頹科之一？"},{"pid":"9c3c28d25ba7dab2ca2bdd0f8904184201efa1f9","tid":317304,"uid":26530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"想屌renee ng 有咩辦法"},{"pid":"8e7d1d33c7f855f0ec51a43e248cbc122e8a6807","tid":317304,"uid":39379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:31:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你邊間書院邊間宿</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用建議黎答你：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚揀聯合書院</span></blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講宿舍生活遠不及崇基(俾我再揀嘅我會揀崇基<br />\n講人文氣息遠不及新亞(其實其他野都一般<br />\n講學生活動遠不及逸夫<br />\n五新就各有千秋啦<br />\n<br />\n但係聯合就幾頭唔到岸<br />\n又要Assemby 又要fyp 靚女又少:(<br />\n<br />\n(雖然宿位係多 但係真係好想住宿嘅 我建議你揀善衡啦)"},{"pid":"9d85b1f67f460e905ce418864df4ac74c8290d23","tid":317304,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"佢地點入 夠入?"},{"pid":"bc4325e073103cd2c148f9ad5591395b858804ca","tid":317304,"uid":39379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會被稱為四大頹科之一？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無頹嘅科 只有頹嘅人(好似我咁<br />\n<br />\n講workload其實就一般<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">正常一個course 都會有tutorial要present 仲有mid term paper或者test 同埋要交final paper </span><br />\n比起理工科係少好多野要做<br />\n但係reading量都好大<br />\n有心讀嘅人會日日刨reading 一啲都唔頹<br />\n唔睇reading嘅就自求多福啦"},{"pid":"83a53ffa55d12e0d0170e6a9cb153b9fc232d28a","tid":317304,"uid":39379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:05:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想屌renee ng 有咩辦法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己Inbox佢"},{"pid":"d2d2f0abdf5cd67383257def03d38384a6a4e99c","tid":317304,"uid":39379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:05:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地點入 夠入?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你up乜鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbb796e24dbfd0ac39f55102ddda3df3087ca94","tid":317304,"uid":122611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:08:09.000Z","msg":"政政多唔多毒撚、八婆同狗公？"},{"pid":"b0e094d71372328860151196f18f8d3059d7b9ca","tid":317304,"uid":54361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:27:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想屌renee ng 有咩辦法</blockquote><br />\n瞓覺"},{"pid":"7d3051d7a8b9a4e0b49f0d7fe5bc3ac8ae40f7cf","tid":317304,"uid":39379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政政多唔多毒撚、八婆同狗公？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁呢層又唔多 我身邊認識嘅政政人都幾好<br />\n係早幾屆有啲好仆街 特別係係學生會活躍個啲"},{"pid":"8aa326c2b2a34a586f14f2d07c8d78d68e448eb8","tid":317304,"uid":126336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:17:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2148ffef80483a9f507a2e79858b443a4426d99b","tid":317304,"uid":74610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><block